     FAW610P0 IF  E           K        DISK                      A
      *今の日時を取得
     C                     CALL 'TIMRS1'
     C                     PARM           P@DATE  80
     C                     PARM           P@TIME  60
      *
     C                     Z-ADD1         P@WEEK
      *当日を含む次の日曜日を取得
     C                     CALL 'DATRG2'
     C                     PARM           P@DATE  80
     C                     PARM           P@WEEK  10
      *
     C                     Z-ADDP@DATE    S1DATE  80
      *
     C           S1DATE    CHAINAW610P0              77
     C   77                WRITEAW610P01
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
